To aboerr:
It's propably because you run FAT32 file system on your computer. You need a disc with NTFS or equally capable system to store files larger than 4Gb. I'd recomend an external / additional harddrive, but otherwise you could look into programs like Partition Magic that's able to convert your partition to NTFS without deleting any data... Hope this helps.
